(SOLUTION \(WHAT IT IS\)) Tj
T*
(Tripable is a ‚Äútrip workspace‚Äù your group shares:) Tj
T*
(- Tabs act like blank pages for brainstorming) Tj
T*
(- Everyone can add options, comment, and vote) Tj
T*
(- The workspace turns decisions into a plan \(dates ‚Üí picks ‚Üí itinerary\)) Tj
T*
ET
