(WORKSPACE MODEL \(CORE IDEA\)) Tj
T*
(Each trip has tabs that behave like canvases:) Tj
T*
(1\) Availability: mark conflicts; see group overlap) Tj
T*
(2\) Places & Activities: add options; attach links; comment; vote) Tj
T*
(3\) Budget: propose ranges; track shared costs; split plan) Tj
T*
(4\) Itinerary: convert winning items into a timeline) Tj
T*
(Design goal: collaborative + less stressful, not ‚Äúone person managing‚Äù) Tj
T*
ET
endstream
endobj
